{
  "stem": "17308.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 23.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then people showed their real colors, their real feelings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anti-Semitic feelings-- but it might be caused to some greed, you know, that-- that some people told that Jews has a better life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think this was one of the causes of anti-Semitism in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, nobody was really happy about the events happening there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But due to the fact that they had a war before, they never expected things to go to that extreme, because Germany occupied Belgium in 1914, '18, and there was nothing anti-Jewish at the time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was worried about the time, but then nobody could expect it would go to that extreme.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they never spoke about leaving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They spoke about the children-- they perhaps should leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When things-- we have family in the United States, and some Jewish families way of thinking about-- not only thinking-- some were sending their children away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the United States.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And other countries also, but mainly United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the parents stayed behind, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When war started?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when war started it was, of course, a-- a big departure immediately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most people who could leave, left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went to France, because this was the first place, where people talked about going, because we always thought that France was a very strong country, and it would be rather safe there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Belgium, as the way it went-- we could see that Belgium couldn't resist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then there was a huge departure towards France as the war started.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Belgium was invaded the 10th of May, 1940, and immediately, people started leaving.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, my family and myself we all left at the 10th of May.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we just closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, bombardment started, and it didn't sound very good.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
